<h2 id="reverting-the-plan-without-proration">Reverting the Plan without Proration <a class="headerlink" href="plan-change-payment-failure#reverting-the-plan-without-proration" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>If this happens, we need to do change the subscription plan <em>back</em> to the original
one: <code>$stripeSubscription-&gt;plan = $originalPlanId</code>. But here's the tricky part: add
<code>$stripeSubscription-&gt;prorate = false</code>:</p>
