<h2 id="telling-the-user-what-happened">Telling the User What Happened <a class="headerlink" href="plan-change-payment-failure#telling-the-user-what-happened" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>That fixes the problem in Stripe. The last thing <em>we</em> need to do is tell the user
what went wrong.</p>
