<p>This will be something like: "Your card was declined".</p>
<p>Oh, and give this a 400 status code so that jQuery knows that this AJAX call has failed.</p>
<p>Finally, in the template, add a <code>.fail()</code> callback with a <code>jqXHR</code> argument:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="97e86f6bfb">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
